OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772305466
OL,3,CAfghan migrant jailed for raping
OL,4,C'vulnerable intoxicated' woman
OL,6,FA migrant from Afghanistan has been
OL,7,Fjailed for 10 years for the rape of a
OL,8,F"vulnerable intoxicated" woman in
OL,9,FSouthampton.
OL,11,FMusafar Hotak, 25, was convicted after
OL,12,Fa trial at Southampton Crown Court of
OL,13,Fthe rape and sexual assault by
OL,14,Fpenetration of the woman in the early
OL,15,Fhours of July 12 2022.
OL,17,FThe court heard that the victim had
OL,18,Fbeen in the Cafe Parfait bar in
OL,19,FSouthampton when she was asked to
OL,20,Fleave by the bouncers for being drunk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
