PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772305466
OL,3,CAfghan migrant jailed for raping
OL,4,C'vulnerable intoxicated' woman
OL,6,FAs she attempted to contact her
OL,7,Fgirlfriend, the defendant, who was 22
OL,8,Fat the time, started to follow her
OL,9,Fbefore a voicemail sent on the
OL,10,Fvictim's phone heard her telling him
OL,11,Fto stop.
OL,13,FThe court was told that the next thing
OL,14,Fthe complainant remembered was waking
OL,15,Fup in Hotak's home with him lying on
OL,16,Ftop of her and sexually assaulting her
OL,17,Fthen raping her.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772305466
OL,3,CAfghan migrant jailed for raping
OL,4,C'vulnerable intoxicated' woman
OL,6,FShe repeatedly told him to stop but
OL,7,Fshe felt unable to prevent him because
OL,8,Fhe was using "a lot of force", the
OL,9,Fcourt heard.
OL,11,FAfter she escaped, she contacted
OL,12,Fpolice and an intimate swab taken from
OL,13,Fher was matched to the defendant's DNA.
OL,15,FReading her personal impact statement
OL,16,Fto the court, the victim said she
OL,17,Flived in "constant fear" and the
OL,18,Fattack had "left scars in every part
OL,19,Fof my life" which had led her to self-
OL,20,Fharm and an attempt to take her own
OL,21,Flife.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772305466
OL,3,CAfghan migrant jailed for raping
OL,4,C'vulnerable intoxicated' woman
OL,6,FShe said: "What happened to me
OL,7,Fdestroyed my life in ways I never
OL,8,Fthought possible. I didn't just feel
OL,9,Fviolated, I felt erased.
OL,11,F"Since that day I have lived in fear,
OL,12,Fshame, silence and unbearable pain
OL,13,Fthat I can't fully describe.
OL,15,F"I was left feeling broken and empty
OL,16,Fand terrified of the world around me."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
