PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772305466
OL,3,CAfghan migrant jailed for raping
OL,4,C'vulnerable intoxicated' woman
OL,6,FJudge Gary Lucie sentenced Hotak to a
OL,7,F10-year prison term with a four-year
OL,8,Fextended period on licence, imposed an
OL,9,Findefinite restraining order on him
OL,10,Fnot to contact the victim, and placed
OL,11,Fhim on the sex offenders' register.
OL,13,FHe told Hotak, who was assisted by a
OL,14,FPashtu interpreter: "The Home Office
OL,15,Fwill consider whether to deport you."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
