PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772305466
OL,3,CAfghan migrant jailed for raping
OL,4,C'vulnerable intoxicated' woman
OL,6,FHe added: "You took advantage of the
OL,7,Fvictim who was very drunk. It is
OL,8,Fobvious your offending has had a
OL,9,Fsevere psychological impact on her
OL,10,Fwhich will probably remain with her
OL,11,Ffor the rest of her life.
OL,13,F"I want to pay tribute to her for her
OL,14,Fbravery in coming forward and going
OL,15,Fthrough what must have been a very
OL,16,Fdifficult time for her."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
